{"tid":265461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[理性討論] 點解要撐Uber","createTime":"2017-05-31T15:39:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T06:49:17.000Z","uid":12287,"like":4,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"493739d1ec2dba8359347045f6d538bc44d351ac","tid":265461,"uid":12287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T15:39:52.000Z","msg":"的士佬係仆街，但人地比錢攞牌交稅揸車<br />\nUber 係私人機構，市值700億美金，<br />\n走法律罅賺錢比人告，真心唔明有乜野好撐<br />\n<br />\n係撐就撐修例放寬Fintech 、金融條例管制，<br />\n容許自動駕駛車，加快推動電動車，推動巴士改用電改善空氣<br />\n依啲就真係推動科技發展啦"},{"pid":"2003d41d5f4d69888036849d38c2ff239ccec77f","tid":265461,"uid":64325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T15:58:26.000Z","msg":"因為10個的士9個服務差手車差揀客"},{"pid":"b9864aa02ee0e058c66d09d2afb9a84e51e1448e","tid":265461,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T15:59:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d644b263021dbd40b9b6b623cf969a7f42a6eeb","tid":265461,"uid":97558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:03:03.000Z","msg":"點解因為私人公司就唔撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 作為消費者梗係想有多個選擇，尤其係香港奉行自由市場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef4973efb528b64a277f9a0e00e4e508b67d6498","tid":265461,"uid":67823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:04:48.000Z","msg":"唔鐘意益啲仆街的士佬唔得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢攞正牌有交稅 唔代表佢好 唔代表要比錢佢賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81cd04e63c638dc91f3b384a01aa494cf746513d","tid":265461,"uid":27032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:07:24.000Z","msg":"撐Uber 就唔可以撐其他科技發展？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n重有作為消費者，的士佬個牌幾貴關我咩事？<br />\n我只係知班的士佬幾咁劣"},{"pid":"383a7edad70469a31b4b7ed18a2b0692d0ba4d6c","tid":265461,"uid":104941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:07:26.000Z","msg":"因為憎的士狗"},{"pid":"a2edf1a1d0dae7d40a3401174ff502240b896ead","tid":265461,"uid":54733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:08:13.000Z","msg":"我想睇的士狗仆街"},{"pid":"f67ed61a3083af342c42e5b0516ae7b774caef98","tid":265461,"uid":33190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:10:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解因為私人公司就唔撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 作為消費者梗係想有多個選擇，尤其係香港奉行自由市場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今日坐的士，個的士佬收多5毫子專登唔找<br />\n我最後冇追，因為我唔計較呢少少錢 但呢個行為絕對令我反感"},{"pid":"5850f013b141f8feb6398b8628f640cb2d7f9ec9","tid":265461,"uid":45832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:10:29.000Z","msg":"點解要坐冇氣袋 Comfort ?"},{"pid":"993dcd604825351a13deeb9b6c52ba56bc9bfd2d","tid":265461,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:11:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ae4ff1afb851a4945cbf1d2da67dbaad8d299cc","tid":265461,"uid":13796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:14:26.000Z","msg":"我只係睇服務，完！<br />\n<br />\n當你有7個人私士比唔到service 我，我可以call 架Uber Black 7 seater<br />\n<br />\n上架的士危險到係highway 玩電話落order 仲可以手寫埋。我上架uber 人地專心揸車有電話仲cut 埋人線。<br />\n<br />\n點比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c49ce27aeba3723da60d683fb4eebcf23b45e7fe","tid":265461,"uid":92871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:14:26.000Z","msg":"唔係撐uber 只係唔想濕鳩政府限制其他競爭者進入市場，維護利益者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f166599eb279def85760551a4c8c6b3efcc5ba8e","tid":265461,"uid":13592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:14:45.000Z","msg":"最憎一台獨大"},{"pid":"4c7f81d1001d7767a599eeb182955bc13f283b4f","tid":265461,"uid":37798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:15:19.000Z","msg":"因為想過海"},{"pid":"ed09687b10ddd960c1df7fbafa3fb80b161d46ef","tid":265461,"uid":59639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:18:06.000Z","msg":"weekend 夜晚的士狗例牌落旗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兜路，近又黑面乜柒都齋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"344a094c4fde6d3ec25e68d2e402d97ae4692442","tid":265461,"uid":108635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:18:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為想過海</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f75fd67f82c0f3b516b08e3cca2245e26cbeed","tid":265461,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:18:20.000Z","msg":"on9<br />\n如果你有成日坐一定唔會咁講<br />\n有d的士佬係好，冇問題<br />\n但一到繁忙時間又唔過海，又尻<br />\n個個星期d人去偏僻地方小費加成150蚊都未必call到一架<br />\n<br />\nuber有加成但都冇咁撚過份"},{"pid":"ab0c33a9c9fb61dc1b88326e53a1d119b3632428","tid":265461,"uid":10975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:19:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>on9<br />\n如果你有成日坐一定唔會咁講<br />\n有d的士佬係好，冇問題<br />\n但一到繁忙時間又唔過海，又尻<br />\n個個星期d人去偏僻地方小費加成150蚊都未必call到一架<br />\n<br />\nuber有加成但都冇咁撚過份</blockquote><br />\n脂肪粒"},{"pid":"2f4db8e7097bc0b62e20f6b8d185a9bf93d8393c","tid":265461,"uid":2993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:21:43.000Z","msg":"車又靚過的士<br />\n平又平過的士<br />\n服務又好過的士<br />\n又唔駛受d的士佬面色<br />\n諗唔到點解唔揀uber<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f62e651bbb3c49c67d2a920fd938c19163e2ff","tid":265461,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:23:24.000Z","msg":"反而fb 果個uber grp<br />\nd 司機狂屌uber 食水深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個都想uber 仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f154653ecca226cd55a279cb572417896c00950","tid":265461,"uid":52576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:29:34.000Z","msg":"點解撐uber?  咁有冇諗過點解uber犯法？ 因為法例過時囉！ 正苦成日話撐科技發展，然後啲法律就一直唔跟住個年代更新，搞到d科技發展受到阻力，香港一味剩係靠金融，係咪金融賺到錢就夠？科技就唔L重要，其他野都唔洗發展？正苦剩係識得做埋d 9屎野去整走d有利我地小市民嘅野，我地想有得揀正苦就唔比我地揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7005b11165ee448bb0602c1f6e5fcb45a667e149","tid":265461,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T17:20:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因為想過海</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n駁唔到"},{"pid":"52dc892504adc4a6c7e934380a4b5bfe45094106","tid":265461,"uid":38343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T01:49:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/v2cx4etq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fv2cx4etq&h=4fe86159&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「拒載，是對緣份的嘲諷。繞路，是對感情的執著。」- 拒載大師<br />\n<br />\n「唔識路喎！」「唔過海喎！」<br />\n的士司機瀟灑地手握軚盤，無情地主宰道路的命運、乘客的命運。<br />\n<br />\n白牌賊匪只懂用虛偽新車涂毒人心，<br />\n的士司機卻能以經典音樂洗滴心靈。<br />\n<br />\n紅色的跑車，像是帶著神秘；<br />\n冚旗的咪錶，彷彿隱藏貞操。<br />\n<br />\n福特的士，舒適同價但不載客；<br />\n潛龍勿用，這樣玄妙你懂不懂。<br />\n<br />\n用 APP 叫車有如電召銷魂，一買一賣過後各走各路，恩斷義絕。<br />\n相反，在街上隨緣截車，經歷多番情感衝激才能上車；<br />\n下車付錢時被強制收多一蚊幾毫，為旅程留下牽絆的印記，何其浪漫。<br />\n<br />\n非法載客取酬無第三者保險，<br />\n泥鯭的團購送客義薄雲天，第三者、第四者、甚至第七者都能感受到司機的愛！<br />\n<br />\n「唔過海」是仁的表現，欺山莫欺水，欺人莫欺心；渡海有違天性。<br />\n「交更呀」是義的表現，防風氏後至，禹殺而戮之；遲到自古是罪。<br />\n「行兩步」是禮的表現，只聞車避城，豈聞城避車；人要謙虛自省。<br />\n「唔識路」是智的表現，知之為知之，不知為不知；賢者心明如鏡。<br />\n<br />\n的士傳承香港文化，司機有品味有智慧敦厚可靠。<br />\n即使你口裡說不，趕時間的話身體卻會誠實上車。"},{"pid":"a52532e01d20d09f9cc26c60082a7f98ba1d56da","tid":265461,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T01:50:04.000Z","msg":"的士狗仆街，完"}]}